WEBVTT

00:00:59.840 --> 00:01:01.040
and percussionist.

00:01:01.400 --> 00:01:06.240
(Applause)

00:01:06.960 --> 00:01:08.896
As I grew up, subconsciously,

00:01:08.920 --> 00:01:13.216
I felt a strong urge
to hide my newfound hobby.

00:01:13.240 --> 00:01:15.536
Even without it being said out loud,

00:01:15.560 --> 00:01:18.880
I knew that somehow
it was wrong to do what I was doing.

00:01:20.680 --> 00:01:22.536
In most of the ceremonies,

00:01:22.560 --> 00:01:26.656
I noticed that most of the women
and girls were not in sight,

00:01:26.680 --> 00:01:28.216
but when they were,

00:01:28.240 --> 00:01:30.776
I noticed that they would wear
their dancing skirts